    <h2 class="termsH">ATTENDANCE AND MAKE-UP POLICIES</h2>
    <p class="termsP">The student must notify the institute 24 hours before the scheduled class to qualify for a make-up  lesson, otherwise, the student will be charged for that lesson and the teacher will be paid. In the event that the student does not show up to the lesson or the student does not cancel the lesson in the required time, this will be counted as a NO SHOW and the teacher will record a make-up video lesson with the contents he/she had prepared for that day. This video lesson will be sent as a link in the clients discord direct message within 48 hours of the scheduled lesson. If cancellation was done on time and a make-up lesson is issued; Gaines opus institute can not guarantee that the lesson will be taught by the student’s chosen instructor. The same attendance and make-up policy applies to make-up lessons, in the event a recorded video lesson will be sent by the instructor who had the make-up lesson scheduled. 
    </p>
    <br />

    <h2 class="termsH">MAKE-UP CLASSES </h2>
    <p class="termsP">Make-up lessons can only be scheduled during the course of active membership or plan. A student must be enrolled and the account must be active to receive Make-up lessons. Make-up lessons may not be used to extend a membership once membership is expired. Make-up lessons can be assigned only once. Make up lessons DO NOT qualify for re-scheduling. If a student needs to cancel or cannot show up for a make-up lesson, no make-up lesson or refund will be given for the not attended make-up lesson. A video lesson recorded by the teacher who was scheduled for the make-up lesson will be sent to the client in the client's discord direct message within 48 hours after the scheduled make-up lesson. 
    </p>
