    <h2 class="termsH">LESSON CANCELLATION AND OUR 100% CREDIT POLICY</h2>
    <p class="termsP">Cancellations don’t apply to lessons scheduled within 24 hours of the lesson. A 24 hours cancellation notice is required to qualify for a make-up lesson. If you need to cancel your class, direct a message to discord to one of the staff to talk to someone from the admin department and process the cancellation. These are the ONLY valid methods for canceling classes. Email cancellations, talking to your instructor about it, and/or calls to our other phone lines are NOT accepted mediums for canceling. In the event the class is not canceled in the required timeframe, the lesson will be marked as a NO SHOW. *Remember NO SHOWS don’t qualify for make-up classes.* We guarantee you will always, 100% of the time, have your credits recognized: If cancellation is done on time, you will qualify for a make-up lesson. If cancellation is not done on time, you will get a personalized video lesson recorded by the teacher explaining the content prepared for that day. This will ensure that you will get the materials for all of the lessons that you paid for. 
    </p>
