    <h2 class="termsH">I. TESTS AND EXAMS:</h2>
    <p class="termsP">Copying from another student during an examination or allowing another to copy your work.
    Using unauthorized notes during a closed book examination.
    Using unauthorized devices, software, websites or apps during an examination.
